reviews.review_text: Great short show Shame about the jam after drums.
less labels (and tracks)! You guys remind me of a kid who's just gotten a Dymo Label Maker (ask your parents) for Christmas. "Door"! "Doorknob"! "Telephone"! "Drums"! "Jam"!
